<h1>Locatii</h1>
In aceasta pagina se pot afla informatii legate de locatiile de imprumut ale obiectelor. Daca ati introdus orasul in detaliile contului, locatiile vor fi ordonate
dupa distanta fata de dumneavoastra.
<br>
<% if admin? %>
  <%= link_to 'Adauga o noua locatie', new_admin_location_path, class: "btn btn-primary" %>
<% end %>
<br>
<div class="row">

<%= paginate @locations %>
<% @locations.each do |location| %>
<div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 mb-4">
    <div class="card h-100 text-center">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h4 class="card-title">
            <%= location.name %>
          </h4>
          <br>
          <p class="card-text"> Adresa: <br>
            <%= "#{location.address}" %> </p>
          <p class="card-text"> Program: <br>
            <%= "#{location.schedule}" %> </p>
          <% unless location.alternative_contact.blank? %>
          <p class="card-text"> Alte metode de contact: <br>
            <%= "#{location.alternative_contact}" %> </p>
          <% end %>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<% end %>
</div>
<br>
<%= paginate @locations %>
